item.title: Jolly Rancher Cool Tubes Review
item.description: Back in the summer of 2013 TheVCubeSolver and I dropped by the local candy shop to review Blue Bunny’s Jolly Rancher Cool Tubes, a push-pop like product in three weird flavors. It turned out to be a complete and total sensory experience.
